xdialog (2.3.1-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * finally uploading new upstream release to unstable (Closes: #383345)
    - double clicking in radiolist and checklists no longer sends one
      mouseclick to the window behind the xdialog window (Closes: #399891)
    - Hidden directories / files can be selected as in the documentation
      described (Closes: #399810)
    - --icon works with --colorsel (Closes: #374481)
  * Updating upstream URL in debian/copyright and debian/control

 -- Alexander Schmehl <tolimar@debian.org>  Tue, 31 Jul 2007 17:51:28 +0200

